track_notes: Returned via a much drier track than the one starting at the Cattle Grid parking spot. This track reaches the road at about SD718483, a couple of hundred yards downhill from the Cattle Grid.

Total time (including ops): 45m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
